<p><strong>AC</strong> 24, touch 11, flat-footed 23 (+10 armor, +1 Dex, +3 shield)<br/><strong>hp</strong> 80 (8d10+32)<br/><strong>Fort</strong> +9, <strong>Ref</strong> +6, <strong>Will</strong> +5; +2 vs. fear<br/><strong>Defensive Abilities</strong> bravery +2</p>
